about-us.title: About Us
about-us.description: Discover the best place to enjoy authentic Himalayan cuisine at Satprayas Nepal! Soon, we will become your favorite spot in the city for genuine Himalayan dishes. Our commitment is to deliver outstanding service and top-quality food.
